<UserControl x:Class="Ripperoni.MVVM.View.AboutView" xml:space="preserve"
             xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
             xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" 
             xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
             mc:Ignorable="d" d:DesignHeight="555" d:DesignWidth="400">
    <Grid>
        <Grid>
            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <ColumnDefinition/>
                <ColumnDefinition Width="5*"/>
            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>

            <StackPanel Margin="10">
                <Image Source="/Images/Ripperoni.png" Margin="5">
                    <Image.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect/>
                    </Image.Effect>
                </Image>
                <Image Source="/Images/Newtonsoft.png" Margin="5">
                    <Image.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect/>
                    </Image.Effect>
                </Image>
                <Image Source="/Images/WebP.png" Margin="5">
                    <Image.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect/>
                    </Image.Effect>
                </Image>
                <Image Source="/Images/YoutubeDL.png" Margin="5">
                    <Image.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect/>
                    </Image.Effect>
                </Image>
                <Image Source="/Images/YTDLP.png" Margin="5">
                    <Image.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect/>
                    </Image.Effect>
                </Image>
                <Image Source="/Images/Downloader.png" Margin="5">
                    <Image.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect/>
                    </Image.Effect>
                </Image>
                <Image Source="/Images/Javi.png" Margin="5">
                    <Image.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect/>
                    </Image.Effect>
                </Image>
            </StackPanel>

            <ScrollViewer VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" Grid.Column="1">
                <StackPanel Margin="10">
                    <TextBlock Background="Transparent" Foreground="White" x:Name="Handle" FontWeight="Bold"
                               TextAlignment="Justify" TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,5,0,5">KPNC Technology: Ripperoni:
                               </TextBlock>

                    <TextBlock Background="Transparent" Foreground="White"
                               TextAlignment="Justify" TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,5,0,5"><Bold>About:</Bold> Ripperoni is an open source project that aims to download online media (mainly from YouTube) quickly. While it mainly serves to download media, it also includes many quality-of-life functionalities.</TextBlock>

                    <TextBlock Background="Transparent" Foreground="White"
                               TextAlignment="Justify" TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,5,0,5"><Bold>Introduction:</Bold> There are four main tabs. In the “Downloads” tab you can see the progress of media being downloaded. In the “Properties” tab you can change the default output folder, the preferred format, and the preferred resolution. In the “Settings” tab you can tune downloader options like temporary file folder, enable memory caching, maximum transfer speed, timeout delay, concurrent threads, reattempts before hard fail, and buffer size. You may also find other custom solutions for fixes with network problems such as those within the Charter Communication network. In the “About” tab you will find this message along with the links to the open source projects used in this application. The lower interface includes the text box where you can input a direct link by clicking the download button or search keywords that will be queried through YouTube Search by clicking the search button. Finally, you may find useful links in the application's footer.</TextBlock> 

                    <TextBlock Background="Transparent" Foreground="White"
                               TextAlignment="Justify" TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,5,0,5"><Bold>Further Information:</Bold> For bug reports, feature requests, documentation, and/or contact information, please check out the project’s repository below...</TextBlock>

                    <Label />
                    <Label Foreground="#007ACC" Content="James Newton-King: Newtonsoft.JSON"
                           x:Name="n" MouseDown="N_MouseDown"/>
                    <Label Foreground="#007ACC" Content="Behzad Khosravifar: Downloader"
                           x:Name="d" MouseDown="D_MouseDown"/>
                    <Label Foreground="#007ACC" Content="Jose M. Piñeiro: WebPWrapper"
                           x:Name="w" MouseDown="W_MouseDown"/>
                    <Label Foreground="#007ACC" Content="Bluegrams: YoutubeDLSharp"
                           x:Name="y" MouseDown="Y_MouseDown"/>
                    <Label Foreground="#007ACC" Content="Jaco Vis: Javi.FFmpeg"
                           x:Name="j" MouseDown="J_MouseDown"/>
                    <Label Foreground="#007ACC" Content="FFmpeg: FFmpeg"
                           x:Name="f" MouseDown="F_MouseDown"/>
                    <Label Foreground="#007ACC" Content="YT-DLP: YT-DLP"
                           x:Name="p" MouseDown="P_MouseDown"/>
                </StackPanel>
            </ScrollViewer>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
</UserControl>

